How to play with the arcade:

    You can move the character with ZQSD
    The R key restarts the current game
    The P key loads the next graphic library
    The U key loads the previous gaphic library
    The M key loads the next game
    The J key loads the previous game
    The X key let you go back to the menu
    The N key exits the program as closing any graphical window will also exit the program